name: SXZ Night Elves [ Warcraft ]
description:
All the content I make is and will be completely free on CivitAI.
But if you want to support me with a coin, then you can do it here.

Trained on AbyssOrangeMix2 with Clip Skip 2.

Sample images was generated with Luma and AOM2

Recommended embeddings:
1. easynegative
2. bad-hands-5
3. badhandv4

Strength 0.6-0.8 is optimal.

PLEASE CHECK YOUR LORA NAME AFTER DOWNLOAD.

Male Night Elf: 1boy, henelf, athletic
Female Night Elf: 1girl, shenelf, athletic

Skin color: grey, purple, blue, dark, pale
Eye color: white, blue, yellow, purple

Also you may improve it with glowing eyes, facial mark

When you using 1boy, henelf or 1girl, shenelf add opposite in negative prompt.
